videos.title: Welcome to Locia Farms - A Peaceful Family Farm in Ocala, Florida
videos.description: Welcome to Locia Farms - a peaceful six-acre hideaway in Morriston, Ocala, Florida. Experience our family farm with goats, chickens, and fresh produce.
videos.transcript:
Video Summary:

• Peaceful Farm Landscape
  Welcome to Locia Farms, a peaceful six-acre hideaway...

• Happy Goats on the Farm
  Our goats roam freely, bringing joy to our daily lives...

• Our Free-Range Chickens
  Fresh eggs come from our happy, free-range chickens...
